{"title_page": "Hello Elephant", "text_new": "{{more citations needed|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Hello Elephant\n| image          =Hello Elephant.jpg\n| caption        =\n| director       =[[Gianni Franciolini]]\n| producer       = [[Vittorio De Sica]]\n| writer         =[[Suso Cecchi d'Amico]]<br> [[Cesare Zavattini]]\n| starring       =\n| music          = [[Alessandro Cicognini]]\n| cinematography =[[Anchise Brizzi]]\n| editing        = [[Eraldo Da Roma]]\n| distributor    =\n| released       = {{Film date|1952}}\n| runtime        = 78 minutes\n| country        = Italy\n| language       = Italian\n| budget         =\n}}\n'''''Hello Elephant''''' ({{lang-it|Buongiorno, elefante!}}) is a 1952 Italian [[comedy film]] directed by [[Gianni Franciolini]].\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Vittorio De Sica]]: Carlo Caretti \n* [[Mar\u00eda Mercader]]: Maria Caretti \n* [[Sabu (actor)|Sabu]]: Sultan of Nagore \n* [[Nando Bruno]]: Mr Venturi, landlord\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|0043986}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hello Elephant}}\n[[Category:1952 films]]\n[[Category:Italian films]]\n[[Category:Italian-language films]]\n[[Category:Films directed by Gianni Franciolini]]\n[[Category:Films with screenplays by Suso Cecchi d'Amico]]\n[[Category:Films with screenplays by Cesare Zavattini]]\n[[Category:Italian comedy films]]\n[[Category:1952 comedy films]]\n{{1950s-Italy-comedy-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{more citations needed|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Hello Elephant\n| image          =Hello Elephant.jpg\n| caption        =\n| director       =[[Gianni Franciolini]]\n| producer       = [[Vittorio De Sica]]\n| writer         =[[Suso Cecchi d'Amico]]<br> [[Cesare Zavattini]]\n| starring       =\n| music          = [[Alessandro Cicognini]]\n| cinematography =[[Anchise Brizzi]]\n| editing        = [[Eraldo Da Roma]]\n| distributor    =\n| released       = {{Film date|1952}}\n| runtime        = 78 minutes\n| country        = Italy\n| language     