e       = Nebraska Wesleyan\n | overall    = 3\u20132\n | confrecord =\n}}\n{{CFB Yearly Record End\n | overall  = 25\u201314\u20131\n | bowls    = no\n | poll     = no\n | polltype = \n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://bentley.umich.edu/athdept/football/coaches/crawford.htm Profile at Bentley Historical Library, University of Michigan Athletics History]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|list =\n{{Michigan Wolverines football coach navbox}}\n{{Wisconsin Badgers football coach navbox}}\n{{Baker Wildcats football coach navbox}}\n{{Nebraska Cornhuskers football coach navbox}}\n{{Texas Longhorns football coach navbox}}\n{{Nebraska Wesleyan Prairie Wolves football coach navbox}}\n}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Crawford, Frank}}\n[[Category:1870 births]]\n[[Category:1963 deaths]]\n[[Category:Baker Wildcats football coaches]]\n[[Category:Michigan Wolverines football coaches]]\n[[Category:Nebraska Cornhuskers football coaches]]\n[[Category:Nebraska Wesleyan Prairie Wolves football coaches]]\n[[Category:Texas Longhorns football coaches]]\n[[Category:Wisconsin Badgers football coaches]]\n[[Category:Creighton University faculty]]\n[[Category:Yale University alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Colebrook, New Hampshire]]\n[[Category:People from Baldwin City, Kansas]]\n", "name_user": "Jweiss11", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:cleanup", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Crawford"}
